		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰化成棘轮，不断朝玩家处滚动，接触造成<span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span>伤害，滚到太边上会破碎暴露核心，持续1-3轮。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰复苏时，召唤1至2层绕其转动的冰墙，每层由3面<span textDecoration="underline">冰墙</span><span>组成，每面冰墙可以承受2个霜之实的攻击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰抛出5个<span textDecoration="underline">霜之实</span><span>，落地造成</span><span color="#99ffff">25%</span><span>伤害，依次落在玩家的中、右、左、右、左处，用重击将霜之实打回无相之冰处以破盾阻止恢复生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="405" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">极冰外壳：<span color="#99ffff">168冻</span><span>盾，击破使无相之冰虚弱。<br/>霜之实：使用重击以启动，命中时</span><span color="#99ffff">-80冻</span><span>。<br/>冰墙：</span><span color="#99ffff">6冻</span><span>盾，用于阻挡霜之实前进，霜之实命中时</span><span color="#99ffff">-3冻</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰脱去外壳，3簇冰棘呈逆时针样围绕其旋转，接触造成<span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span>伤害，另有在圈外追踪玩家的冰棘，同样造成</span><span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="442" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰生命值低于5%时进行复苏，收拢并形成<span textDecoration="underline" color="#99ffff">极冰外壳</span><span>，复苏持续30s，当复苏次数为</span><span color="#99ffff">1/2/&gt;2</span><span>时，无相之冰每3s恢复</span><span color="#99ffff">5%/2.5%/1.25%</span><span>生命值，最大恢复至</span><span color="#99ffff">50%/25%/12.5%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
