		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰开阵，8个冰立方外壳围一圈暴露核心，从上到下发射8根追踪玩家的冰锥，每个冰锥造成<span color="#99ffff">50%</span><span>伤害；冰锥发射一段时间后，将分裂成3个更细的冰针，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">25%,10%,2.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2686a2" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2686a2">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之冰%B7奏鸣曲%B7霜锐之阵.assets/Image_20.png')" x="596" y="427" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之冰%B7奏鸣曲%B7霜锐之阵.assets/Image_21.png')" x="576" y="406" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之冰悬于空中，向地面连续轰炸冰刺，共轰炸3次，每次造成<span color="#99ffff">100%</span><span>伤害，第三次轰炸留下霜覆地面，接触造成</span><span color="#99ffff">30%</span><span>伤害；技能持续期间将持续随机抛出冰针，造成</span><span color="#99ffff">25%,10%,2.5%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
